I dropped out. I'm done.

45
00:03:24,705 --> 00:03:26,438
Are you insane?

46
00:03:26,440 --> 00:03:27,773
You've never been.

47
00:03:27,775 --> 00:03:29,741
Trust me, college
is just another...

48
00:03:29,743 --> 00:03:31,743
Lame-ass pyramid scheme.

49
00:03:31,745 --> 00:03:34,646
They hand you a free ride out
of this place, and you just

50
00:03:34,648 --> 00:03:37,449
Throw it away? Please don't.
This-this is about us.
This is not about...

51
00:03:37,451 --> 00:03:40,752
No, angie, just listen to me
for a second, all right?
I...

52
00:03:40,754 --> 00:03:42,854
Hey, hey, hey.

53
00:03:42,856 --> 00:03:44,923
Hey.

54
00:03:46,226 --> 00:03:49,428
I have loved you
since the third grade.

55
00:03:50,396 --> 00:03:52,731
You're the only person

56
00:03:52,733 --> 00:03:55,567
In the whole world
who knows the real me.

57
00:03:57,503 --> 00:04:00,672
And that's why
I can't be with you.

58
00:04:00,674 --> 00:04:02,908
Look, I'm gonna
be late for work.

59
00:04:02,910 --> 00:04:04,977
Why are you acting like this?

60
00:04:06,846 --> 00:04:07,879
Hey.
Ow!

61
00:04:38,278 --> 00:04:40,545
Mrs. Grinnell?

62
00:04:40,547 --> 00:04:42,814
Julia shumway.

63
00:04:42,816 --> 00:04:46,351
