64
00:04:46,353 --> 00:04:48,353
So you're the newspaper woman?

65
00:04:48,355 --> 00:04:50,689
I'm the new editor
of   <i>the independent</i>yeah.

66
00:04:50,691 --> 00:04:53,025
But if you're just having
a problem with your delivery,

67
00:04:53,027 --> 00:04:55,894
You can go ahead and...
I get my news online,
sweetheart,

68
00:04:55,896 --> 00:04:57,296
Like everybody else.

69
