its emergency reserves.

85
00:05:36,670 --> 00:05:38,570
Here's the thing:

86
00:05:38,572 --> 00:05:40,472
When duke told me,

87
00:05:40,474 --> 00:05:42,441
He sounded nervous.

88
00:05:43,409 --> 00:05:44,976
Believe me,

89
00:05:44,978 --> 00:05:48,680
That man's never sounded nervous
a day in his life.

90
00:05:50,883 --> 00:05:52,951
Okay.

91
00:05:55,888 --> 00:05:57,622
I'll do some digging.

92
00:05:58,691 --> 00:06:00,926
