taking all our trucks?

95
00:06:36,764 --> 00:06:38,163
Over to westlake.
It's parade day.

96
00:06:39,166 --> 00:06:41,533
I love you, too, rusty!

97
00:06:43,537 --> 00:06:44,770
Duke:
<i>Never understand</i>

98
00:06:44,772 --> 00:06:46,972
Why you said yes
to one of those meatheads.

99
00:06:46,974 --> 00:06:50,609
'cause their insurance policy
makes ours look like crap.

100
00:06:50,611 --> 00:06:52,177
man: <i>No!</i>

101
00:06:52,179 --> 00:06:54,179
I'm headed back now.
Hey, listen...

102
00:06:54,181 --> 00:06:56,848
So, we got a problem here.
Your guy...

103
