119
00:10:50,183 --> 00:10:52,717
wh-what happened?

120
00:10:54,887 --> 00:10:56,821
Whoa.

121
00:10:58,991 --> 00:11:00,325
Hey. No. Don't touch that.

122
00:11:00,327 --> 00:11:03,395
holy crap.

123
00:11:05,798 --> 00:11:07,365
What is it?

124
00:11:11,704 --> 00:11:14,105
