125
00:11:16,742 --> 00:11:18,777
Are you sure you're okay, duke?
Yeah. Yeah.

126
00:11:18,779 --> 00:11:20,111
My damn pacemaker.

127
00:11:20,113 --> 00:11:21,813
Must've skipped a beat.

128
00:11:21,815 --> 00:11:23,848
