158
00:13:24,471 --> 00:13:25,837
From the bank.

159
00:13:25,839 --> 00:13:28,239
She sponsored our
little league team.

160
00:13:33,245 --> 00:13:34,412
No.

161
00:13:34,414 --> 00:13:36,114
No, no, no. Hey!

162
00:13:38,083 --> 00:13:40,118
Hey! Stop the truck!

163
00:13:40,120 --> 00:13:42,921
Wait-- if it crashes
through, you're dead.
Stop! Stop!

164
00:13:43,889 --> 00:13:45,123
Stop the truck!

165
00:13:46,559 --> 00:13:48,026
Stop!

166
00:13:52,965 --> 00:13:54,332
