Call the faa.

170
00:14:03,176 --> 00:14:05,009
The feds?
Yes.

171
00:14:05,011 --> 00:14:07,846
They got to shut down
this whole airspace.
Uh, okay,

172
00:14:07,848 --> 00:14:10,415
What if the government
built this thing?

173
00:14:11,383 --> 00:14:13,151
I doubt it.

174
00:14:13,153 --> 00:14:14,953
Why?

175
00:14:16,623 --> 00:14:19,157
'cause it works.

176
00:14:21,293 --> 00:14:24,562
man: <i>Sorry</i>
<i>for the radio silence, folks.</i>

177
00:14:24,564 --> 00:14:26,898
<i>Generator's cooking</i>
<i>and we're up and running again.</i>

178
00:14:26,900 --> 00:14:30,134
I'm phil bushey,
and you're listening to wybs,

179
00:14:30,136 --> 00:14:37,876
The mill's only 100%
independent home of rock.

180
00:14:37,878 --> 00:14:39,911
Phil.
dodee, hey.

181
00:14:39,913 --> 00:14:41,246
We're the only thing
on air right now--

182
00:14:41,248 --> 00:14:43,548
Am, fm, anywhere.

183
00:14:43,550 --> 00:14:44,949
Yeah, the blackout, I know.

184
00:14:44,951 --> 00:14:46,417
No, even if that
were statewide,

185
00:14:46,419 --> 00:14:48,887
Every station our size has
its own generator, so...

186
00:14:48,889 --> 00:14:51,422
Why is the whole dial
still static?

187
00:14:51,424 --> 00:14:53,491
I don't know.

188
00:14:53,493 --> 00:14:57,896
But our ratings
are gonna be <i>amazing.</i>

189
00:15:05,604 --> 00:15:07,438
Duke: What the hell
happened here?

190
00:15:07,440 --> 00:15:08,940
Sheriff perkins!

191
00:15:08,942 --> 00:15:10,308
The plane smashed right into it.

192
00:15:10,310 --> 00:15:12,510
I was almost killed.
Th-this man saved my life.

193
00:15:12,512 --> 00:15:14,579
Slow down, son.
Slow down.

194
00:15:14,581 --> 00:15:16,414
You hurt?

195
00:15:16,416 --> 00:15:20,685
I think something just, uh,
clipped me on the way down.

196
00:15:20,687 --> 00:15:22,520
Linda:
Why aren't the guys

197
00:15:22,522 --> 00:15:24,055
Putting out the fires?

198
00:15:24,057 --> 00:15:24,989
Duke:
You saw it crash.

199
00:15:24,991 --> 00:15:26,257
Into what?

200
00:15:26,259 --> 00:15:27,525
I don't know, but, I mean,

201
00:15:27,527 --> 00:15:28,526
Whatever this thing is,

202
00:15:28,528 --> 00:15:30,194
