203
00:15:30,196 --> 00:15:31,429
Young man:
It's like a wall.

204
00:15:31,431 --> 00:15:33,498
You just can't see it.

205
00:15:33,500 --> 00:15:34,399
Rusty.

206
00:15:34,401 --> 00:15:36,367
Rusty.

207
00:15:36,369 --> 00:15:37,368
I don't think
he can hear you.

208
00:15:37,370 --> 00:15:39,037
god!

209
00:15:41,340 --> 00:15:43,341
Baby, you okay?

210
00:15:43,343 --> 00:15:47,011
I-I can't hear you.

211
00:15:50,250 --> 00:15:51,983
Step away from there, linda.

212
00:15:51,985 --> 00:15:53,484
I don't understand.

213
00:15:53,486 --> 00:15:55,019
What is it?

214
00:16:02,328 --> 00:16:03,661
Watch your step, jim.

215
00:16:03,663 --> 00:16:05,563
That's chuck thomson's plane,
isn't it?

216
00:16:05,565 --> 00:16:07,532
Not anymore.

217
00:16:07,534 --> 00:16:09,067
Paul:
Hey, duke?

218
00:16:09,069 --> 00:16:11,669
We got a real bad accident
on pretty valley.

219
00:16:11,671 --> 00:16:13,204
Duke, it's freddy.

220
00:16:13,206 --> 00:16:15,073
I've got one, too,
over on motton.

221
00:16:15,075 --> 00:16:17,408
A minivan versus...
I don't know what,

222
00:16:17,410 --> 00:16:19,477
But the thing's flat as a dime.

223
00:16:19,479 --> 00:16:21,479
Whole family's doa.

224
00:16:21,481 --> 00:16:22,714
Linda:
Whatever it is,

225
00:16:22,716 --> 00:16:25,717
