227
00:16:28,722 --> 00:16:31,255
The whole town.

228
00:16:37,162 --> 00:16:40,131
We're trapped.

229
00:16:47,072 --> 00:16:48,740
Big jim: Okay, here's what
we got: There's 19 roads

230
00:16:48,742 --> 00:16:50,441
Going in and out
of chester's mill.

231
00:16:50,443 --> 00:16:51,642
Not including the dirt ones.

232
00:16:51,644 --> 00:16:53,277
Joe, would you go home
and stay there?

233
00:16:53,279 --> 00:16:55,146
Duke: Paul and freddy
are setting up

234
