to button up the whole town.

236
00:16:59,085 --> 00:17:00,184
Big jim:
Eh, do what you can.

237
00:17:00,186 --> 00:17:02,186
I got a contingency plan.

238
00:17:03,356 --> 00:17:05,156
No, no, no, julia.
This is a crime scene.

239
00:17:05,158 --> 00:17:07,458
Julia: No. Plane falls out
of the sky, that's news.
Big jim: Hey!

240
00:17:07,460 --> 00:17:09,060
I'm the ranking
official here,

241
00:17:09,062 --> 00:17:10,061
And I'm ordering you to leave.

242
00:17:10,063 --> 00:17:11,529
Jim!
We got bigger fish to fry.

243
00:17:11,531 --> 00:17:13,598
Linda, you commandeer
ms. Shumway's vehicle.

244
00:17:13,600 --> 00:17:14,766
