245
00:17:14,768 --> 00:17:16,667
What the hell? That's my car!

246
00:17:30,816 --> 00:17:32,683
Who the hell are you?

247
00:17:35,688 --> 00:17:38,623
Barbie.

248
00:17:38,625 --> 00:17:41,125
People just call me barbie.

249
00:17:41,127 --> 00:17:43,061
Barbie?

250
00:17:43,063 --> 00:17:44,495
It's a nickname.

251
00:17:44,497 --> 00:17:46,564
Anyway, I'm not your story.

252
00:17:47,566 --> 00:17:49,767
Then why don't you show me
what is.

253
00:17:55,742 --> 00:17:58,309
Am I doing something wrong?
Power's out, carolyn.

254
00:17:58,311 --> 00:18:01,079
Cashier said the pumps will be
back on soon.

255
00:18:01,081 --> 00:18:04,348
"is known for its rich,
fertile land

256
00:18:04,350 --> 00:18:06,117
And warm, inviting people."

257
00:18:06,119 --> 00:18:08,586
Please, these jerks don't even
have orange juice.

258
00:18:08,588 --> 00:18:11,255
Guy said we'd have to wait
till the next delivery.
Carolyn: Alice,

259
00:18:11,257 --> 00:18:13,758
You didn't take your
insulin without eating.

260
00:18:13,760 --> 00:18:16,227
I'll be fine.
I got a candy bar.

261
00:18:16,229 --> 00:18:18,796
No...
you need real food, honey.

262
00:18:18,798 --> 00:18:21,666
We'll stop at that
